1263
01:15:39.486 --> 01:15:42.886
To put this in context, it is important to note that MSS

1264
01:15:42.926 --> 01:15:46.246
colorectal cancer is a cold tumor characterized by an

1265
01:15:46.286 --> 01:15:48.606
