1268
01:15:57.486 --> 01:15:58.066
changes,

1269
01:15:59.306 --> 01:16:03.226
as well as other immunosuppressive tumor microenvironment factors.

1270
01:16:04.666 --> 01:16:08.486
In this context, single-agent checkpoint inhibitors that target

1271
01:16:08.566 --> 01:16:11.226
PD-1 or PD-L1 have no activity.

1272
01:16:13.046 --> 01:16:16.266
Limited activity is noted when we combine

1273
01:16:16.346 --> 01:16:19.046
