One of the major strengths of the presentation by Dr.

1277
01:16:30.086 --> 01:16:33.606
Melero is the outstanding scientific rationale.

1278
01:16:34.746 --> 01:16:38.346
So, bispecific T-cell engagers have had limited

1279
01:16:38.446 --> 01:16:42.326
success in solid tumors, and this is due to a multitude

1280
01:16:42.386 --> 01:16:45.726
of reasons, some of which are listed here: low and

1281
01:16:45.766 --> 01:16:49.146
heterogeneous antigen expression, limited tumor

1282
01:16:49.206 --> 01:16:53.156
accessibility, and low levels of T-cell infiltration in

1283
01:16:53.206 --> 01:16:54.686
