1288
01:17:09.906 --> 01:17:13.486
sufficient in the suppressed tumor microenvironment

1289
01:17:13.566 --> 01:17:15.666
of MSS colorectal cancer.

1290
01:17:16.726 --> 01:17:20.426
So this is where the second co-stimulation signal from

