evaluated in the CAR T setting.

1296
01:17:38.766 --> 01:17:42.086
Another important factor to note is that the conditional

1297
01:17:42.166 --> 01:17:46.106
activation of 4-1BB that requires co-binding

1298
01:17:46.146 --> 01:17:49.016
to FAP is important in reducing

1299
01:17:49.086 --> 01:17:52.586
toxicity that has historically been seen to the

1300
01:17:52.625 --> 01:17:56.125
